text: Edwin Ongchuan is a Filipino politician from the 2nd district province of Northern Samar in the Philippines. He is currently serves as a Governor of Northern Samar. He was first elected as Governor of the province in 2019. He also currently serves as a member of House of Representatives of the Philippines. ==References== * * * * ==External links== *Province of Northern Samar Category:Living people Category:1968 births Category:Governors of Northern Samar Category:PDP–Laban politicians
